Looking for a Toyota RAV4 near Washington?

The Toyota RAV4 was one of the first modern crossover utility vehicles, and since its redesign in 2013, it's been an excellent fit for the habits of its most common buyers -- families who want a fuel-efficient, reliable, easy-to-park vehicle. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect RAV4 for you.

Autotrader has 38,160 Toyota RAV4s for sale near Washington, DC, including a Certified 2017 Toyota RAV4 AWD XLE, a Certified 2017 Toyota RAV4 FWD LE, and a Certified 2017 Toyota RAV4 Limited.

Not sure if a RAV4 is the right fit for you?
